The '''Apple''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] grown by planting an [[Apple Sapling]], waiting 28 days for it to grow into an [[Apple Tree]], and harvesting the tree during the [[Fall]].

An Apple may be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|100}} or found in [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]], if the fruit bat option is chosen.

