==Tailoring==
Apple can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Relaxed Fit Pants]].[[File:Relaxed Fit Pants.png|36px]] It can be also used as a red dye color at the dye pots in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Apple is not used in any [[quests]].

==Trivia==
* Despite their in-game description, they can neither be turned into juice nor cider. When placed in a [[Keg]] to be turned into a drink, an Apple will instead produce [[Wine|Apple Wine]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

